</style><p>（ <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="1/\lambda^4"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">4</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>部分对小<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>蓝光的影响大于对大<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>红光的影响）。我们还展示了这样的日落图片： </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:66.68%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/cn70nijalvjgyoydsdlc" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/cgauwakm2pzczysjlzrh 110w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/oywj3277a1gtoq71ewgr 220w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/vohodnhibcswtzjcvqdc 330w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/xcikos736s33iqgixlce 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/dqrqy02rifqxt3fq3emd 550w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/ffmgqtciwhhplj8mr2j7 660w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/zyxcwyhnzdg7wkfblrzx 770w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/prcfpu9pntihmuvtpxdi 880w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/ykjq61v8xsegc9ia7a1c 990w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/uu8peffyzfck6kryo71c 1024w"></figure><p>演示直通红光和反射蓝光的效果。</p><p>所以最后，“为什么天空是蓝色的？”</p><p>答：“因为夕阳是红色的！”</p><p> “为什么日落是红色的……？”</p><p>这是可以理解的。一件事只能用另一件事来解释。但即使我们有时间详细了解瑞利散射，他们也可以合理地问：“为什么光会根据该公式发生散射？”我们可以更深入地用麦克斯韦方程组解释瑞利勋爵的证明。为什么麦克斯韦方程组呢？嗯，量子电动力学，这是一种具有局域<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="U(1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>规范对称性的量子场论，也就是说空间中的每个点都有一个额外的自由度，类似于第四个空间维度，只不过这个维度不能像其他三个维度一样在正常空间中旋转，这个维度作为一个圆连接到自身而不是无限的（这就是<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circle_group">U</a> <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="U(1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circle_group">意思</a>），并且 3D 空间中的相邻点尝试最小化这个额外参数的差异，这导致波浪。解释力是惊人的：如果你假设存在这种<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="U(1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>对称性，你实际上可以推导出光子一定存在。但为什么会有<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="U(1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>对称性呢？</p><p>现代物理学似乎痴迷于对称性。即使这种<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="U(1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>对称性也可以用<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electroweak_interaction#Formulation">更基本的</a><span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="SU(2)\times U(1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.032em;">S</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">×</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （不同的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="U(1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ）和希格斯机制来解释。物理学家似乎保持沉默，避免说“这是最基本的事情”，而是说“这一件事实际上是另一件事的表现”。回答“为什么光子存在？”这个问题。 “因为空间具有内部<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="U(1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>对称性”有点像说“天空是蓝色的，因为日落是红色的”。</p><p>对称性解释将我们对世界的描述折叠成更小的描述。他们说，一件事在数学上可以从另一件事推导出来，也许可以在两个方向上推导，但他们根本没有说明为什么其中任何一个都会存在。也许这是一个无法回答的问题，而对称语言是承认这种局限性的一种方式。</p><p>为了说明我的意思，请考虑一个仅由完美圆正中心的点组成的宇宙。 （自从一次演讲中教授写下“ <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\psi(\mbox{universe})"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">ψ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mstyle"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">宇宙</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ”并说“物理学的目标是找到宇宙的波函数”以来，我一直可以随意地说“考虑一个宇宙……” ，”伴随着一阵紧张的笑声和拖着脚的声音。）</p><p>这是一个二维世界，因此我们可以使用笛卡尔坐标<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="y"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>来定位该空间中的点。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:60.17%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/swnshwnhczenfm0rvial" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/kmv6ijhe7rrapobvkk15 120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/boior2vgj1dvcqquat6y 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/hgnctexaxriisfhl2bpk 280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/thndr97ssffxbufrqcwi 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/rfb7sf4zlt8twenvacah 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/ynqeswfqdh4ozjip9gyh 520w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/w8g5uoxonmak50cekw0f 600w"></figure><p>然而，由于旋转对称性， <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="y"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>说得太多了。任何点<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="(x, y)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>与另一个点<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="(x', y')"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-msup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mo" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">&#39;</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-msup MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.006em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0.082em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mo" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">&#39;</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>完全无法区分，其中</p><span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\left(\begin{array}{c} x' \\ y' \end{array}\right) = \left(\begin{array}{c c} \cos \phi &amp; -\sin \phi \\ \sin \phi &amp; \cos \phi \end{array}\right) \left(\begin{array}{c} x \\ y \end{array}\right)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size3-R" style="padding-top: 1.256em; padding-bottom: 1.256em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mtable" style="vertical-align: -0.965em; padding: 0px 0.167em;"><span class="mjx-table"><span class="mjx-mtr" style="height: 1.2em;"><span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px; width: 0.802em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="margin-top: -0.2em;"><span class="mjx-msup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mo" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">′</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mtr" style="height: 1.23em;"><span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0.2em 0px 0px 0px;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="margin-top: -0.2em;"><span class="mjx-msup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.006em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0.082em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mo" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">′</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size3-R" style="padding-top: 1.256em; padding-bottom: 1.256em;">)</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mrow MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size3-R" style="padding-top: 1.256em; padding-bottom: 1.256em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mtable" style="vertical-align: -0.98em; padding: 0px 0.167em;"><span class="mjx-table"><span class="mjx-mtr" style="height: 1.23em;"><span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0px 0.5em 0px 0px; width: 2.101em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="margin-top: -0.2em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">余弦</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">φ</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; width: 2.935em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="margin-top: -0.2em;"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">-</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">罪恶</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">φ</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mtr" style="height: 1.23em;"><span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0.2em 0.5em 0px 0px;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="margin-top: -0.2em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">罪</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">φ</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0.2em 0px 0px 0.5em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="margin-top: -0.2em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">因斯</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">φ</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size3-R" style="padding-top: 1.256em; padding-bottom: 1.256em;">)</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mrow MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size3-R" style="padding-top: 1.256em; padding-bottom: 1.256em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mtable" style="vertical-align: -0.965em; padding: 0px 0.167em;"><span class="mjx-table"><span class="mjx-mtr" style="height: 1.2em;"><span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px; width: 0.572em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="margin-top: -0.2em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mtr" style="height: 1.23em;"><span class="mjx-mtd" style="padding: 0.2em 0px 0px 0px;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style="margin-top: -0.2em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size3-R" style="padding-top: 1.256em; padding-bottom: 1.256em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>对于任意<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\phi"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">ψ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。让我们用极坐标<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="r = \sqrt{x^2 + y^2}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-msqrt MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.045em;"><span class="mjx-surd"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.593em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">√</span></span> <span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.084em; border-top: 1px solid;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.409em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.006em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.409em; padding-left: 0.082em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\phi = \tan^{-1}(y/x)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">phi</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">tan</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.519em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>重新表述一下<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\phi = \tan^{-1}(y/x)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ： </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:51.22%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/hx8ib85kwfuyikxodczt" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/edrdxjrkxqbbj9qc0ba6 120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/oqjgep0pi1lfwkpy3l3u 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/pcnpy3lgbb1fz3fqsefv 280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/kkweb4d0von5hwhzcwvu 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/ygjqmowrovonocqawtll 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/ue2btcdtagtefzwzgs2a 520w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/jyqmooxctcewx5huznf3 600w"></figure><p>现在我们可以看到<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\phi"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">是</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>一个多余的坐标。请记住，圆是完全光滑的（不是由粒状原子组成）并且它完全以点为中心。如果沿<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\phi"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">ψ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>方向的运动无法以任何方式观察到，那么它就不是物理事物；没有任何实验可以揭示我们正在以<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\phi"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">ψ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>移动。</p><p>这个宇宙实际上只是由一端有界的一维空间中的两个点组成。或者进一步说，这个宇宙中除了距离之外什么都不存在，距离是一个量化这两个点之间距离的数字（没有任何东西可以与该距离进行比较）。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:33.06%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/qds0cryqk5uywjy1zlog" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/dryump9js42kmi7i9gib 120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/g1z6s1ced531rtohw7ne 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/tk4sthezwjapzkn3do2o 280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/ltluf4lyvbdblhroez1h 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/lvlydlwkfglnmb8ocstw 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/szrdsydfagrlgkwmbsy0 520w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/q0mldhodnleba08op8o8 600w"></figure><p>不服气？假设我们朝另一个方向前进——我们不删除多余的坐标，而是添加多余的坐标。给定二维圆，假设我说还有另一个坐标<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="z"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">z</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，我们实际上看到的是一个无限圆柱体。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:67.84%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/wljmuxjbzqofbjiadiip" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/ktynfnm0ggcles0buk49 120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/bihwcyvhrfpfnwxrwvr2 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/gnslsdqmtkitb2rv4vd5 280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/za9uavh5pgyw7xxjkcfd 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/u8pvo7z5hqpnblprtdeq 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/jlyragp7ux2fhsvniivz 520w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/jmcksgpuywpr1fueztmr 600w"></figure><p>我可以继续添加多余的坐标，但我可以弥补的内容没有任何限制。唯一独特的描述是对要描述的事物进行收缩包装的描述。 （或者，如果不是唯一的，则为一小组等效表示中的一个。）唯一性（或接近唯一性）使其变得有趣。或者更确切地说，缺乏自由使它变得有趣：数学比页面上的随机符号更有趣，因为它有限制。</p><p>这就是为什么物理学正在走向统一：当我们用一件事来描述另一件事时，我们就取得了最大的进步，这样它们似乎就不再是两个不同的事物了。如果你想到“为什么天空是蓝色的？”和“为什么日落是红色的？”作为两个不相关的问题，世界似乎比已知的同一问题的两个方面更加复杂和任意。</p><p>这又回到了<a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/i8C9KSryDFj4EENvx/reality-and-reality-boxes#Reality_3__causality__and_reasons_why_in_general_">之前的一篇文章，我在这篇文章中认为原因（以及一般意义上的原因）与物理现实是不同的</a>。在物理现实中，蓝天和红色日落之间存在着深刻的联系，但两者互不造成，也不是由第三种事物造成的。尽管人们习惯说“蓝天和红晚都是由瑞利散射造成的”，但如果我们从字面上理解，这句话就没有任何意义。</p><p>从字面上看，这意味着“没有瑞利散射，就不会有蓝天或红色日落”（对于排他原因；根据概率和多重原因进行必要的修改）。我们会想象一个有瑞利散射的世界和一个没有瑞利散射的世界，只有有瑞利散射的世界才有蓝色的天空和红色的日落。如果我们不进一步思考“没有瑞利散射”将意味着麦克斯韦方程组是错误的（假设数学推导没有错误），并且一个与麦克斯韦方程组不同的世界将是一个非常好的世界，那就太好了。不同的世界。</p><p>当物理学还处于起步阶段时，这些事情可能是可以想象的，当时人们发现事物之间存在如此多的联系，改变一个事物意味着许多其他事物的变化，除了前沿领域，比如极高的能量或强引力场。但现在我们已经到了这个地步，一切似乎都可以从标准模型和广义相对论推导出来，除了这两种理论预计不适用的前沿之外，没有太多回旋余地。</p><p>然而，讨论原因<i>是</i>有意义的，特别是在不太了解的领域，例如人类行为。这就是为什么我将谈论原因（以及其他原因）与实际发生的事情分开，并将它们放在不同的<a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/i8C9KSryDFj4EENvx/reality-and-reality-boxes">现实盒子</a>中。我们甚至使用不同的动词时态来描述这些事物：虚拟语气表示原因——如果原因发生，<i>将会是</i>什么——以及简单现在时表示物理现实。</p><p>原因和理由——为什么是物理现实之上的一层，我们对物理现实的说法是基于我们不完全的理解，以及我们如何想象它可能会有所不同——原则上，如果不是事实上的话。它也受到限制：我们不能说任何事情都是原因。即使是更宽松定义的原因，例如叙述和神话，也可能是错误的。只要有可能出错，它就会很有趣！</p><br/><br/><a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/the-goal-of-physics#comments">讨论</a>; https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmK/the-goal-of-physicals N6gGz3KjFcGjiZZmKJim Pivarski Sat, 02 Sep 2023 23:08:02 GMT 
